title: State v. Chester Hollman III – Episode 3 – Testilying
description:
February 19, 2018 / Rabia, Susan and Colin examine the witness recantations, and their impact in court, in the murder case against Chester Hollman III. 

"Dawkins and Jones, 2017" PC: Philadelphia Inquirer

Episode scoring music by Animal Weapon, Blue Dot Sessions.
